.. _Common Dylan and Functional Extensions library reference: /static/documentation/opendylan/core/index.htm
.. _System and I/O library reference: /static/documentation/opendylan/io/index.htm
.. _Building Applications Using DUIM: /static/documentation/opendylan/dguide/index.htm
.. _DUIM library reference: /static/documentation/opendylan/dref/index.htm
.. _C FFI: /static/documentation/opendylan/interop1/intero_4.htm
